    "However, as the scores were often discussed in natural language, where the information (type of test, date of test, and test scores) can be far apart from each other, traditional NLP methods are not viable for this particular task without extensive efforts and large amount of training samples.",
    "We have included a few examples of clinical texts in S2",
    "Table to demonstrate the heterogeneity of the texts.",
    "In this diagnostic/prognostic study of ChatGPT and LlaMA-2 for extracting cognitive exam dates and scores from clinical notes, ChatGPT exhibited high accuracy in extracting MMSE scores and dates, with better performance compared to LlaMA-2.",
    "The use of LLMs could benefit dementia research and clinical care, by identifying eligible patients for treatments initialization or clinical trial enrollments."
